OL,3,CBone found in search for Muriel Mckay
OL,4,Cconfirmed to be non-human
OL,6,FA bone has been found in the search
OL,7,Ffor Muriel McKay, her family have told
OL,8,FITV News.
OL,10,FMuriel McKay was taken in 1969 after
OL,11,Fcriminals wrongly thought she was
OL,12,Fmedia mogul Rupert Murdoch's then-
OL,13,Fwife, and planned to demand a #1m
OL,14,Fransom.
OL,16,FShe was actually the wife of Mr
OL,17,FMurdoch's deputy Alick McKay. Two men
OL,18,Fwere jailed for murder but Ms McKay's
OL,19,Fbody has never been found.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
