OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1774098665
OL,3,CBone found in search for Muriel Mckay
OL,4,Cconfirmed to be non-human
OL,6,FHer family believed her remains were
OL,7,Fburied in a garden in East London.
OL,9,FHowever, Metropolitan Police have
OL,10,Fconfirmed the bone found on 20 March
OL,11,Fdoes not belong to a human.
OL,13,FThe search came after a scan of the
OL,14,Farea on Bethnal Green Road was carried
OL,15,Fout 5 March 2026 which revealed two
OL,16,Fsignificant anomalies.
OL,18,FOne of them was in the location
OL,19,Fidentified by a key witness, Ms Hayley
OL,20,FFrais.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
