FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1774098665
OL,3,CBone found in search for Muriel Mckay
OL,4,Cconfirmed to be non-human
OL,6,FThe family had believed it could be
OL,7,Fthe remains of Ms McKay.
OL,9,FThe Metropolitan Police and the
OL,10,FCoroner were notified as soon as the
OL,11,Fdiscovery was made.
OL,13,FIt was previously thought that the
OL,14,Fremains of Mrs McKay could be at a
OL,15,Ffarm in Stocking Pelham,
OL,16,FHertfordshire, after one of her
OL,17,Fabductors offered information.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
