CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1774098665
OL,3,CBone found in search for Muriel Mckay
OL,4,Cconfirmed to be non-human
OL,6,FThe farm was searched at the time,
OL,7,Fagain in 2022, and most recently in
OL,8,FJuly last year, but no remains were
OL,9,Ffound.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/5
